snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Say Hello To Mai! Fighting Pass
snippet.description:
Sting like a bee with the Say Hello to Mai! Fighting Pass on February 5!

Get avatar gear inspired by Mai's outfit and roam World Tour and Battle Hub looking for your next obsession. There's also a snazzy Challenger Screen effect and the Flame Dragon God (Nippon Stage II) music to celebrate Mai's arrival in Street Fighter 6.

https://www.streetfighter.com/6/
